- Walking barefoot across the circles of <span style="color:#00afef;">[[Level 142]]</span> reportedly increases the likelihood of accidental transition.

- Standing on circles matching one’s clothing color for extended periods may rarely trigger transportation.
===<span style="color:#fff212;">Exits</span>===
